creator: IBP App-Development
descriptionHtml:
SmartHDM is a family of intelligent sensors, sensor-modules and interfaces for the maintenance of medical devices as well as measuring tasks in the laboratory and environment.

Android devices combined with highly developed SmatHDM software results in a completely new type of measuring system with features and a high level of accuracy simply not achievable with other units.
